    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i'm still kinda a bit nauseous too which is annoying. but u think it's definitely just dehydration? i've heard about people having bad migraines that feel like that. is it safe to just take some ibuprofen and sleep it off for a few hours then? i have a big exam tomorrow so i really need to just get through this.",
